Class PartitionedMobCompactionRequest.CompactionPartition

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.mob.compactions.PartitionedMobCompactionRequest.CompactionPartition
  • Enclosing class:
    PartitionedMobCompactionRequest

    protected static class PartitionedMobCompactionRequest.CompactionPartition
extends Object
    The partition in the mob compaction. The mob files that have the same start key and date in their names belong to the same partition.
